### ===================================================================
### 2-QADAM: LITSENZIYA YUKLASH
### Vazifa: Advokat litsenziyasini (PDF yoki Rasm) serverga yuklash.
### MUHIM: Ushbu .http fayl turgan papkada "license.pdf" degan fayl bo'lishi shart! (Yoki nomini o'zgartiring).
### Eslatma: Javobdan qaytgan fayl ID sini (masalan uuid) olib, yuqoridagi @licenseAttachId ga qoying.
### ===================================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/attach/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI5OTg5MTE1NzY3NzciLCJyb2xlcyI6IlJPTEVfVVNFUiIsImlkIjoiMyIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTc3ODYwNywiZXhwIjoxNzgxODY1MDA3fQ.3kbaU7yZLJNZetX9JI_VNfHO2jIAJng-lMFMdF0krKTU-Mfhu_qACsiLR5fmBvzsTo7q4upbKpK8OuOPRYyWww

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="license.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./license.pdf
--WebAppBoundary--

