### ===================================================================
### DIQQAT: 7, 8, 9, 10-QADAMLAR UCHUN ODDIY FOYDALANUVCHI TOKENI KERAK!
### Yana 1-qadamga borib, oddiy mijoz (User) logini bilan kiring va @token ni yangilang.
### ===================================================================

### ===================================================================
### 7-QADAM: MIJOZ - ADVOKATLAR KATALOGINI KO'RISH
### Vazifa: Mijoz qidiruv orqali faol (APPROVED) advokatlarni izlaydi.
### ===================================================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyers/public?page=1&size=10&region=Toshkent
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===================================================================
### 8-QADAM: MIJOZ - ADVOKAT PROFILINI OCHISH
### Vazifa: Mijoz aniq bir advokatning to'liq ma'lumoti va litsenziyasini ko'radi.
### ===================================================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyers/public/{{lawyerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===================================================================
### 9-QADAM: MIJOZ - ADVOKAT BILAN CHAT BOSHLASH
### Vazifa: Mijoz tanlangan advokatga o'zining birinchi xabarini yuboradi.
### Eslatma: Javobdan qaytgan "id" (Chat ID) ni olib, yuqoridagi @lawyerChatId ga qo'ying.
### ===================================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats/start
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "lawyerId": {{lawyerId}},
  "message": {
    "content": "Assalomu alaykum, meros masalasida maslahat kerak. Ishni ololasizmi?"
  }
}

### ===================================================================
### 10-QADAM: CHATNI YOPISH
### Vazifa: Mijoz yoki Advokat o'zaro chatni yopishi (yakunlashi).
### ===================================================================
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/lawyer-chats/{{lawyerChatId}}/close
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}